title: **Thank you for choosing Returned Studios**
description:
All you have to do now is wait till a team member responds to your request.
There might be a delay with response because of time zones.
We thank you for your patience, understanding and for choosing our services.

Note that by creating a commission request and communicating with us through this channel, you are assumed to have accepted our [Terms of Service](https://returnedstudios.notion.site/Terms-of-Service-9c0768d1192a44e88d63bcc0394c732f)
